B.PG=new A.hO(B.GI,"Bug Fixing & Optimization","Diagnose and resolve complex bugs, improve app responsiveness, and optimize overall performance. Conducted unit, widget, and integration testing using flutter_test and Mockito for reliable bug-free releases. Achieved 80% reduction in real-time data update lag through optimized sync logic. Proficient in performance profiling, memory management, and reducing app load times across Android and iOS platforms.")
